core.title: Sweet Dreams Garden Tent for WellieWisher Dolls
core.global_title_tag: Sweet Dreams Garden Tent for WellieWishers™ Dolls | American Girl
core.global_description_tag: The WellieWishers gather in this fabric tent imagining that they're deep in the woods. Includes lantern, graham crackers, marshmallows, chocolate, and s'more.
core.product_auxdescription: Sweet Dreams Garden Tent for WellieWisher Dolls

images.alt: Sweet Dreams Garden Tent for WellieWisher Dolls

attributes.MarketingDescription:
When the sun sets, the WellieWishers gather in this nighttime hideaway imagining that they're deep in the woods—and naturally, pretend camping is sweeter with the fixings for campfire treats. This set includes:
  • A bright fabric tent with a whimsical night scene
  • A vine-decked lantern to light the WellieWishers' way
  • A box of pretend graham crackers
  • A bag of pretend marshmallows
  • A stick for roasting them
  • A faux chocolate bar
  • A faux s'more
attributes.Tab2ContentCSR:
• Tent: Plastic/polyester - Play tent has simple A-line construction with rods and connectors. Rods are encased in fabric and connectors are tacked to the tent. Opening end of tent has firefly print on mesh or sheer nylon. Firefly print on opening flap and tent are glow in the dark. Ruffles on both ends of tent. It measures 16.5" W x 11" D x 12" H - The tent will accomodate two Wellie Wishers
  • Care instructions: Wipe clean with damp cloth
  • Lantern: Molded plastic - Intermittent LED lights, 3 button-cell batteries (included)
  • Bag of marshmallows: Plastic - Molded marshmallows with permanently sealed clear plastic bag around them>/li>
  • Box of Graham crackers:Card stock - the box does not open
  • Stick: Chocolate bar, S'more: Molded plastic
attributes.PLAgoogleprodcat: Toys & Games > Toys > Dolls, Playsets & Toy Figures > Toy Playsets

attributes.MarketingDescription:
The WellieWishers adore watching flickering fireflies in Aunt Miranda's garden, and afterward, they 're ready to slip on these cute PJs. Includes:
  • A nightie with a cute and colorful firefly pattern, featuring ruffles on the sleeves and hem
  • Knit slippers
  • 2 matching hairbands
attributes.PLAgoogleprodcat: Toys & Games > Toys > Dolls, Playsets & Toy Figures > Doll & Action Figure Accessories
attributes.Tab2ContentCSR:
• Nightie: 100% Cotton/Velcro/plastic, the buttons are non-functioning. Nightie has a Velcro back closure
  • Care Instructions: Hand wash in cold water, line dry
  • Slipper socks: 100% Cotton uppers/:100& polyurethane outsole, slip ons - feature faux leather soles, ruffles along the top
  • Care Instructions: Wipe clean with damp cloth
  • Hairbands (2): 100% nylon

core.global_description_tag: Be ready for the Tooth Fairy with this tooth fairy pillow! The fabric has an image of the WellieWishers Playhouse; a felt door opens to reveals a pocket for her tooth.

attributes.MarketingDescription: When your little one loses a tooth, she'll be all ready for the nighttime sprite to work her magic with this perfect pillow. The fabric has cute tooth appliques and an image of the WellieWishers Playhouse; a felt door opens to reveal a pocket for her teensy tooth! A sweet poem describes the enchanting exchange that will take place in the night.
